data.description: Spacious home located on large lot with mature trees in Candlewick Lake!  Enjoy the lake, fitness center, golf, pool and activities.  Open floor plan on the main level with tons of cabinets and breakfast bar.  1/2 bathroom off the kitchen.  Open staircase leads to 2nd floor family room/loft area and 2 full bedrooms.  The bathrooms are uniquely designed so everybody can get ready at once.  Separated sinks from main area for vanity purposes.  2nd floor laundry in one of the bathrooms.  Large bedroom has balcony overlooking beautiful back yard. Tankless water heater.
